</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Estimation for general birth-death processes</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Crawford%20FW"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Forrest W Crawford</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Forrest W Crawford</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Biostatistics, Yale University, 60 College Street, Box 208034, New Haven, CT 06510 USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Crawford%20FW"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Forrest W Crawford</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Minin%20VN"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Vladimir N Minin</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3><span class="name western">Vladimir N Minin</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Statistics, University of Washington, Padelford Hall C-315, Box 354322, Seattle, WA 98195-4322 USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Minin%20VN"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Vladimir N Minin</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Suchard%20MA"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Marc A Suchard</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3><span class="name western">Marc A Suchard</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>3</sup>Department of Biomathematics, University of California Los Angeles, 6558 Gonda Building, Los Angeles, CA 90095-1766 USA</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>4</sup>Department of Biostatistics, University of California Los Angeles, 6558 Gonda Building, Los Angeles, CA 90095-1766 USA</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>5</sup>Department of Human Genetics, University of California Los Angeles, 6558 Gonda Building, Los Angeles, CA 90095-1766 USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Suchard%20MA"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Marc A Suchard</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>3,</sup><sup>4,</sup><sup>5</sup>
</div>
<ul class="d-buttons inline-list">
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="aip_a" aria-expanded="false">Author information</button></li>
